c quan tr\\u1ecdng, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n v\\u1edbi n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t t\\u1ed1t \\u0111&amp;atilde; nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ef1 quan t&amp;acirc;m l\\u1edbn c\\u1ee7a c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 th\\u1ef1c s\\u1ef1. Trong giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n n&amp;agrave;y, ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i t\\u1eadp trung \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 v&amp;agrave;o c&amp;aacute;c m&amp;atilde; HPG v&amp;agrave; GAS, qu\\u1ea3 ng\\u1ecdt \\u0111&amp;atilde; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h&amp;aacute;i sau m\\u1ed9t th\\u1eddi gian ch\\u1edd \\u0111\\u1ee3i, trong \\u0111&amp;oacute; v\\u1edbi WB116 ri&amp;ecirc;ng HPG mang v\\u1ec1 kho\\u1ea3n l\\u1ee3i nhu\\u1eadn 36.81%, c&amp;ograve;n GAS mang v\\u1ec1 kho\\u1ea3n l\\u1ee3i nhu\\u1eadn 27.20%. N\\u1ebfu kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;aacute;n \\u0111i qu&amp;aacute; s\\u1edbm, c\\u1ea3 hai m&amp;atilde; HPG v&amp;agrave; GAS \\u0111&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; th\\u1ec3 mang v\\u1ec1 c&amp;aacute;c kho\\u1ea3n l\\u1ee3i nhu\\u1eadn kh\\u1ed5ng l\\u1ed3 l&amp;ecirc;n \\u0111\\u1ebfn tr&amp;ecirc;n 100%.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n\\r\\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;1. HPG: C&amp;ocirc;ng ty CP T\\u1eadp \\u0111o&amp;agrave;n H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t l&amp;agrave; m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng doanh nghi\\u1ec7p t\\u01b0 nh&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u Vi\\u1ec7t Nam, chi\\u1ebfm th\\u1ecb ph\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u1edbn trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c kinh doanh th&amp;eacute;p. Trong v&amp;ograve;ng 5 n\\u0103m qua, doanh thu c&amp;ocirc;ng ty c&amp;oacute; b\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u0103ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd v&amp;agrave; v\\u1eefng ch\\u1eafc, t\\u1eeb m\\u1ee9c 17.000 t\\u1ef7 n\\u0103m 2012 \\u0111&amp;atilde; t\\u0103ng v\\u1ecdt l&amp;ecirc;n 33.000 t\\u1ef7 n\\u0103m 2016, k&amp;eacute;o theo \\u01